  "text": "More recently, Peterat et al. [CITATION_1] determined the OUR of S. cerevisiae in a vertical microbubble column with a working volume of 70 μL. The OUR was calculated from the variance in DO when the gas flow was on and a quasi-steady-state of oxygen concentration occurred, or from a dynamic DO profile when the gas flow is interrupted.",
